@startuml CoreNeedleBiopsy_Workflow_Sequence
title Szenario 1: Einfacher Pathologie-Auftrag (Happy Path)\nCore Needle Biopsy – Placer-Filler Kommunikation

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #555555
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #555555
skinparam sequenceGroupBorderColor #AAAAAA
skinparam sequenceGroupFontSize 11
skinparam noteFontSize 10
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF8DC

participant "**Placer (KIS)**\nUrologie" as Placer #BDD7EE
participant "**Filler (LIS)**\nPathologie" as Filler #C6EFCE

== Auftragserstellung (2024-01-15, 08:00) ==

Placer -> Filler : POST Bundle (type: **transaction**)\n  Patient\n  ServiceRequest (status: **active**, intent: order)\n  Specimen [x12] (status: **available**)\n  Task (status: **requested**, code: fulfill)\n\n  Task.focus -> ServiceRequest\n  Task.input -> Specimen[01-12]
activate Filler
Filler --> Placer : Bundle (type: **transaction-response**)\n  201 Created (x15)
deactivate Filler

note over Placer, Filler : **Task V1: requested**\nauthoredOn: 2024-01-15T08:00\nlastModified: 2024-01-15T08:00

== Probenempfang & Annahme (2024-01-15, 14:00) ==

Filler -> Filler : Proben pruefen:\n12 Stanzen in Formalin,\nalle korrekt beschriftet

Filler -> Placer : PUT Task\n(status: **accepted**\nexecutionPeriod.start: 2024-01-15T14:00)
activate Placer
Placer --> Filler : 200 OK
deactivate Placer

note over Placer, Filler : **Task V2: accepted**\nlastModified: 2024-01-15T14:00\nexecutionPeriod.start gesetzt

== Bearbeitung beginnt (2024-01-16, 08:00) ==

Filler -> Placer : PUT Task\n(status: **in-progress**)
activate Placer
Placer --> Filler : 200 OK
deactivate Placer

note over Placer, Filler : **Task V3: in-progress**\nlastModified: 2024-01-16T08:00

group Pathologische Aufarbeitung [3-5 Tage]
  Filler -> Filler : Makroskopie
  Filler -> Filler : Mikroskopie
  Filler -> Filler : Diagnostische Schlussfolgerung
end

== Befunderstellung & Abschluss (2024-01-20, 15:30) ==

Filler -> Placer : POST Bundle (type: **document**, signed)\n  Composition\n  DiagnosticReport (status: **final**)\n  Patient, ServiceRequest, Specimen [x36]\n  Observations (Grouper + Findings)\n  identifier: E_24_001
activate Placer
Placer --> Filler : 201 Created
deactivate Placer

Filler -> Placer : PUT Task\n(status: **completed**\nexecutionPeriod.end: 2024-01-20T15:30\noutput: Bundle)
activate Placer
Placer --> Filler : 200 OK
deactivate Placer

note over Placer, Filler : **Task V4: completed**\nlastModified: 2024-01-20T15:30\nexecutionPeriod.end gesetzt\noutput: DiagnosticReport

== Befund im KIS verfuegbar ==

Placer -> Placer : ServiceRequest\n(status: **completed**)

note over Placer : Befund im KIS verfuegbar.\nKlinische Entscheidung:\nIndikation zur radikalen\nProstatektomie.

@enduml
